          Escherichia <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">coli DH5α cells</ENAMEX> were
          used for cloning mutated 
          ars3002 <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">plasmids</ENAMEX>. The 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">S.</ENAMEX> pombe strain 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">ura4- D18</ENAMEX> ( 
