          leu1-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">32</NUMEX> end1 <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">h -</ENAMEX>) [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">21</TIMEX>] was used as
          the recipient strain for transformation assays. Cells
          were grown at <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">30°C</NUMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">EMM</ENAMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">22</TIMEX>] supplemented with uracil
          and leucine (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">150 mg</NUMEX> each per liter) when not under
