          To construct the plasmid, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">pUra4script</TIMEX>: 
          ars3002 (ext), which contains the
          extended <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">~1.2</NUMEX> kbp 
          ars3002 [ <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">7</ENAMEX>], the <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">~1</NUMEX> kbp 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Eco</ENAMEX> RI fragment containing the
