          <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Cla I and</ENAMEX> 
          Hin cII to produce the <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">~400-bp</ENAMEX>
          fragment containing the enhancer [ <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">7</ENAMEX>]. The gel-purified
          ~<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">400</NUMEX>-bp fragment was inserted into the 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Cla I and</ENAMEX> 
          Hin cII sites of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">p3002PCR</TIMEX> (the
